CodeDef urlencode Filter
CodeDef urlencode Description URL encode
CodeDef urlencode Routine <<EOR
sub {
	my $val = shift;
	$val =~ s|([^\w:])|sprintf "%%%02x", ord $1|eg;
	return $val;
}
EOR
